A heartfelt track that talks about the bliss of having your loved one beside you. Through poetic lyrics and a blend of lo-fi and R&B sounds, the song offers a fresh perspective on admiration and appreciation. With its intimate melodies and soulful vibe, it captivates listeners, leaving a lasting impression of love and affection.
